    {
      "id": "8a9409aa-4fd2-4f64-8f4b-97f6ea94a35f",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "Knowledge tracing is an important in student modelling as it is an application that infers knowledge states and allows the prediction of sucess in future questions based on past questions. A limitation of the current knowledge tracing methods is the way question-response pairings are reporesented. ",
      "raw": {
        "object": "block",
        "id": "8a9409aa-4fd2-4f64-8f4b-97f6ea94a35f",
