    {
      "id": "fca944d6-323e-433d-8b7e-b2a93548d863",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "The authors start with an analysis that identifies cross effects between question-respponse pairs within a sequence of anwers. Then, the authors create a multi-relational transformer for knowledge tracing that better encodes question-reponse pairings. Results show that the new Transformer model outperforms state-of-the-art is four widely-used datasets for knowledge tracing. ",
